        pricing_overview: '<p>Nabla Copilot generally offers a free tier or trial with a limited number of consultations per month to allow clinicians to test the ambient engine. Professional usage requires a monthly subscription per provider, which unlocks unlimited consultations, advanced EHR integrations, and customized note templating.</p>',
        comparison_summary: '<p>Nabla Copilot competes in the specialized "Ambient Clinical Voice" sector against titans like Nuance DAX (by Microsoft) and Abridge. Nuance DAX is a massive, highly expensive enterprise solution deeply embedded in Epic systems. Nabla differentiates itself by being more lightweight, possessing a highly user-friendly interface, and leaning heavily on its strict "zero data retention" policy, appealing strongly to privacy-conscious clinics and physicians seeking rapid, independent deployment.</p>'
