        pricing_overview: '<p>Perplexity operates a highly generous Freemium model. The core search engine is completely free to use, making it incredibly accessible for general queries. "Perplexity Pro" is a standard monthly SaaS subscription targeting power users, researchers, and professionals. The Pro tier unlocks unlimited usage of premium models (GPT-4, Claude 3), the "Copilot" guided search feature, massive file uploads, and priority processing during high traffic.</p>',
        comparison_summary: '<p>Perplexity AI is locked in an existential war against Google Search, Microsoft Copilot (Bing Chat), and standard ChatGPT. Google represents the legacy paradigm. ChatGPT is a brilliant conversationalist but its web search module can feel clumsy. Microsoft Copilot is deeply integrated into Windows. Perplexity differentiates itself by being the ultimate, specialized *Truth Engine*. It doesn\'t want to write you a poem, and it doesn\'t want to sell you ads. Its entire, singular obsession is finding the exact, verifiable answer to your question on the live internet and citing its sources perfectly, making it the beloved tool of modern researchers.</p>'
